EN: We have the same opinion on this issue.

ZH: 这两个事件之间存在相同之处。
EN: There are similarities between these two events.

ZH: 我们兴趣相同，所以我们成为了好朋友。
EN: We have the same interests, that's why we became good friends.

ZH: 这两部电影的结局相同。
EN: The endings of these two movies are the same.

ZH: 在这个案例中，他们的陈述是相同的。
EN: In this case, their statements are the same.

ZH: 这两个方案有相同的设计元素。
EN: These two proposals have the same design elements.

